        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "B) I don't know about this plan of yours."
            }
          ],
          "color": "red"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Although you can\u2019t help today, you spend some time speaking with her about her ambitions toward flight. Discard Dace, and write"
